  nodes.h         <- Emu68 include/nodes.h
  lists.h         <- Emu68 include/lists.h
  md5.h           <- Emu68 include/md5.h

  The three [J5a] runtime couplings are bridged by OUR (AROS-licensed, NON-MPL) files:
    hosted/jit68k/j5c_shims.c  — HOOK 2 cache_read_16 (big-endian fetch from the host
                                 stream, splicing back the 32-bit-truncated address) +
